Package com.ubudu.sdk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UbuduArea
    Interface represents Ubudu Area.
    UbuduAreaDelegate
    The delegate used by the SDK to send area messages to the application.
    UbuduAreaDelegateNotifyUserForEventCallback
    Callback interface allowing to delay notifying the SDK that it should notify user for event.
    UbuduBeacon
    Instances of UbuduBeacon represent actual beacons detected.
    UbuduBeaconRegion
    Interface which extends UbuduArea for beacons.
    UbuduBeaconRegionEvent
    Interface which extends UbuduEvent for beacons.
    UbuduDelayedCustomEventHandlingAreaDelegate
    Extension of the default UbuduAreaDelegate interface.
    UbuduEvent
    Interface that describes UbuduEvent.
    UbuduGeofence
    Interface which extends UbuduArea for geofencing.
    UbuduGeofenceEvent
    Interface which extends UbuduEvent for geofences.
    UbuduOpenInterval
    Interface that describes opening and closing times.
    UbuduOpenInterval.UbuduInterval
    Opening and closing times are given symbolically as a day of the week and hour:minute in the local time zone.
    UbuduRangedBeaconsNotifier
    Notifier called when beacons were successfully ranged in the given proximity UUID.
    UbuduRule
    Interface of a beacon rule object.
    UbuduRule.Action
    The interface of the beacon's rule action object.
    UbuduRule.Antecedant  
    UbuduUser
    UbuduUser instances hold user information.
